Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.31,0:02:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All the pirates who are after the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.71,0:02:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...head for the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.17,0:02:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,except for Gold Roger, the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.46,0:02:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The New World has ruined many pirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.44,0:03:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.15,0:03:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,a boy whose body turned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the Straw Hats finally entered the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the harshest sea ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,After receiving an emergency signal, they landed on Punk Hazard;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,an island with two parts, one burning, the other frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.78,0:03:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A branch of the Navy - G-5 - led by Smoker
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,reached the island while chasing after the Straw Hats
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and got into a fight with Trafalgar Law who appeared out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.29,0:03:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you! Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your help the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Shambles!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he just do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is some mastermind behind Law
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:04:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and if "CC" are his initials,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I know who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the former colleague of Dr.Vegapunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a scientist named Caesar Clown!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:22.84,B1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"The Worst in the World! A Scientist of Terror - Caesar!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Caesar Clown?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I have something on my mind, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,there were a lot of child abduction cases taking place around here recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.53,0:04:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Child abduction?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.98,0:05:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I can't get used seeing you like that, Captain-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped! You have to deal with it for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.67,0:05:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tashigi! What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't heard about any child abductions!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please button up, Smoker-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I like how open that Captain-chan is but she's scary inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All I know is accidents at sea happen frequently in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But in fact, I was wondering why accidents involving children are so prevalent here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.53,0:05:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, that's true, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually go to the communication department often...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.97,0:05:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't have glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.26,0:05:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've heard the G-5 gets many child abduction reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But when it appears in the newspaper, it's often labeled
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,an accident at sea or the work of pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...or simply a child gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.57,0:06:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it could be the reporter's mistake but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I thought maybe it's possible that they were really...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it hard to say, Tashigi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.28,0:06:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's what you think, just say it clearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw a bunch of kids earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're thinking maybe there really have been many abductions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And you think the kidnapper is on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But if that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,those news articles were false...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.43,0:06:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...meaning somebody in the G-5 covered up those child abduction cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.73,0:06:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:07:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it mean somebody among us is working for the kidnapper?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Smo-san, don't insult us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we are a spoiled group in the Navy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but we take pride in being Navy soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right! None of us is doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.28,0:07:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You fools are not even worth suspecting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.34,0:07:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But, all of you guys, don't expect too much from the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.97,0:07:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as it consists of a group of people,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no organization that is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you assume too much, you'll miss the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be fooled by appearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger, Captain-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind, fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm the Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We got fooled by their appearances!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Smoker-san, I'm not so sure about my theory though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay. We'd better keep it in mind anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But since my heart and body are in Law's hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,One third of you should leave here by ship, to make a report.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Vice Admiral?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Our warship's been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.42,0:08:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I saw their ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Steal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! I hadn't thought of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a bad person!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful! Before it gets too late,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to take back my heart and body,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and reveal who's really behind this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:03.46,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1)}VEGAPUNK'S FORMER THIRD LABORATORY
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.13,0:09:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally got through to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats, G-5, and Foxfire Kin'emon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter who dies on this island,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Joker will make it look like an accident at sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch as many of them as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.06,0:09:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The more guinea pigs, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.41,0:09:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.24,0:09:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can just kill the ones who can't be taken with poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did Law go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He left the room a few minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the enemies has a 400-million-berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.05,0:09:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The other members are in a broad range of 120 million to 50 berries each.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.84,0:09:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them are wanted pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and their bounties are 800 million 50 berries in total.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But they have been inactive over the past two years
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:09:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,so their bounty hasn't moved up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.08,0:10:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They could be more powerful than the numbers show.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You always study hard, Monet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what happened to you? It's extremely cold and you didn't wear a coat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We were robbed by some pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.79,0:10:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, they took Boss Brownbeard with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.31,0:10:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really? I'm sorry to hear that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about Brownbeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get him back at any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.68,0:10:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to the backroom now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We just made a new medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.02,0:10:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It will warm up your body and heal your wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.63,0:10:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?! That'd be nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help the others, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.07,0:10:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But first, you have to get treated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.04,0:11:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this, Usopp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of super!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.55,0:11:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It spoils Nami-san's beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.96,0:11:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We get confused if nothing is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Brownbeard?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.08,0:11:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm sure you heard that name before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.00,0:11:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That was what I used to go by.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding, you fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.80,0:11:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away, brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.26,0:11:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you? You were clammed up a while ago
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but now you're talkative.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.97,0:11:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Law's gonna come to save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I despise pirates from your generation
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but Law is an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean our generation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know anything, fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Eleven rookies with bounties over 100 million
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,who arrived at Sabaody at the same time two years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,plus Blackbeard...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.33,0:12:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,People call you twelve "the Worst Generation."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You twelve are troublemakers...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...who were born at the change of the era
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and hold the key to the future of this war-torn world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,After Whitebeard died, you all came to the New World and raised havoc.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When something big happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,there was always somebody from your generation involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Blackbeard! Kid! Law! Drake! Hawkins!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Basil Hawkins was the one who shattered my pirate group.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.74,0:12:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost both of my legs and ended my career as a pirate thanks to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My crew were annihilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.79,0:12:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I fled for my life and arrived here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...on Punk Hazard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.42,0:12:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what this place is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.89,0:12:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This place... This island...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...used to be a lush green treasure house of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing like that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.75,0:13:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And it housed a laboratory
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,of Dr.Vegapunk, a Government scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.55,0:13:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They were experimenting with and developing weapons and chemicals here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of going to prisons, they brought some prisoners here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.04,0:13:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and performed experiments on them like they were guinea pigs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.98,0:13:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But four years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Vegapunk's chemical weapon test went wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And two of the three laboratories exploded!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the remains of that laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:52.87,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1)}THE REMAINS OF VEGAPUNK'S FORMER FIRST AND SECOND LABORATORY
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So there was a huge explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why this place is a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.28,0:15:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The explosion belched intense heat and toxic substances,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and killed each and every living thing on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But in that critical situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the Government left those guinea-pig prisoners
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and escaped from the island then shut it down completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.81,0:15:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The prisoners stayed in the Third Laboratory,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.78,0:15:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the only building that remained intact,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and sheltered themselves from the poison gas that was all over the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Even those who survived were paralyzed mainly in their lower body
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.04,0:15:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the nerve gas
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:16:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and lost hope in their future.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.49,0:16:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...a year later,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.20,0:16:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,our merciful Master came to the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He purified the gas all over the island with his special ability
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and gave those prisoners who couldn't walk mechanical means to move
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.94,0:16:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and took them on as his lackeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.62,0:16:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.41,0:16:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Master-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I landed here a year later after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.52,0:16:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There were still some toxic substances left in the air
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and I felt nauseous when I breathed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:17:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when I thought I had no energy left to live and this was the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the prisoners who lost their legs like I did
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.20,0:17:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,His kindness saved my life as it did to the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.58,0:17:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Vegapunk was a devil because he paralyzed my comrade's legs
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but the Master was our warm-hearted savior!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And then a few months ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the second savior--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Trafalgar Law who had gained the title of Warlord...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...came to the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:18:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Using his special ability,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,he gave those of us who couldn't walk as we wished, legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The legs of living animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought we would never walk again
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.79,0:18:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,so we couldn't stop crying from happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What a touching story!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Tra-guy is a good guy as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He saved my life, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Vegapunk is a horrible person!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.45,0:18:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why there were those half-sheep people at the laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.41,0:18:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Centaurs and the bird woman, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.58,0:18:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It all makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But wait. What about the dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, did you see the dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an artificial being that Vegapunk created to guard the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.82,0:18:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It can adapt itself to any kind of environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard some Celestial Dragon liked it and named it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot the name but if you see it, you better run.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:19:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's extremely aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We already ate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, now you know who rules the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.84,0:19:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No one wants to come near it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Punk Hazard is our Master's property now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.23,0:19:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Rejoice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.48,0:19:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The Master is still doing research today for the future of mankind!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He needs only a few guinea pigs and you can become one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.80,0:19:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Master! I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...medicine is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.74,0:19:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:20:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Get me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.89,0:20:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.82,0:20:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling nauseous and coughing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a headache?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.12,0:20:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels like it's gonna split open!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.08,0:20:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What? It wasn't Vegapunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Smo-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,who caused that huge explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.61,0:20:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who made the weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and let it go off accidentally...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.23,0:20:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...was Caesar Clown!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.82,0:20:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Caesar Clown was
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the second-in-command in the science department at that time
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.99,0:20:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but since he had an inhumane streak,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,he was always butting heads with Vegapunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.59,0:20:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.06,0:20:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How are your eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.88,0:21:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.37,0:21:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... there is... a giant snake in the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.05,0:21:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.43,0:21:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, that's good. Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When the accident happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Vegapunk's name came up only because he was a person in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.71,0:21:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.92,0:21:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,it was a crime to develop a mass-killing weapon that belches poison gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.54,0:21:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And since it had been brought to light by the accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.96,0:21:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Caesar got arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.37,0:21:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But with his formidable ability,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.59,0:21:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,he managed to escape from a prison ship
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and had been missing ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.73,0:21:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If Caesar is still doing research on this island,
